Usage: create_analysis_view [-help] -constraint_mode <modeName>
                            -delay_corner <dcCornerObj> -name <viewName>

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
-constraint_mode <modeName>            # Specifies the name of the constraint
                                       # mode to associate with this analysis
                                       # view (string, required)
-delay_corner <dcCornerObj>            # Specifies the name of the delay
                                       # calculation corner object to associate
                                       # with this analysis view
                                       # (string, required)
-name <viewName>                       # Specifies the name of the analysis
                                       # view being defined (string, required)